# Portfolio Website Project (Homepage, Work, About, Contact)

This is my repo for my Portfolio Website, showcasing my works and different projects in a fun, interactive way.  
The site is built with semantic HTML5, responsive SASS/CSS styling, and JavaScript for animations and interactive features.  

** Pages ** 
Homepage : Hero section with intro animation and smooth navigation.  
About Page : A short introduction about myself and my interests, with a drag-and-drop interactive feature.   
Skills Page: A fun drag-and-drop section to showcase my skills in an interactive way.  
Work Page : A showcase of my featured projects in a grid-based layout. 
Contact Page: Contact form and details to reach me.  

## Features 
Responsive Layout : Optimized CSS Grid design that scales across mobile, tablet, and desktop.  
SASS Styling : Organized with variables, nesting, and partials for cleaner code.  
Hero Animation : Animated text and elements on page load for visual impact.  
Scroll Effects : Sections fade in and stagger while scrolling.  
Interactive Navigation : Mobile menu opens and closes with animation.  
Drag-and-Drop (About Page) : Interactive feature to explore information in a fun way.  
Drag-and-Drop (Skills Page) : Engaging activity to showcase skills interactively.  

## Installation
No installation required. Download the ZIP file and extract its contents. 

## Usage
Open index.html in any modern browser.  
- Scroll through the homepage to see animations and effects.  
- Visit the pages using the menu.  
- Try out the drag-and-drop feature for a fun interactive experience. 

